data.description: Beautifully updated spacious brick bungalow on almost a ½ acre lot in S. Redford. This home features beautifully refinished hardwood floors throughout the first level, a natural fireplace in your spacious living room with custom built-in wall unit. Kitchen recently remodeled with white cabinetry and newer stainless appliances. Your finished basement offers a great entertaining space with a 2nd full bathroom, bar, rec room and pool table (that stays). Your primary bedroom located on the second floor gives you added privacy, plenty of closet space, along with a seating area. There is a long circular driveway, that features an oversized two car garage. This home sits on a corner lot, has great curb appeal and out door space. Welcome Home!
